{
  "texts": [
    "The methodology of this study involves a detailed approach to integrating deep learning and symbolic reasoning within the TinyLlama architecture.",
    "This process encompasses the design of the model architecture, preparation and processing of data, and a comprehensive training and evaluation protocol.",
    "The integration aims to synergize the intuitive pattern recognition capabilities of deep learning with the structured, logical processing of symbolic reasoning, enhancing the model's overall efficacy in information retrieval.",
    "Model ArchitectureOur improved TinyLlama's architecture is illustrated in Figure 1, and conceptualized as an intricate hybrid model, synthesizing the robust features of deep learning with the logical rigor of symbolic reasoning.",
    "Central to this architecture is a transformer-based neural network, N, which effectively processes extensive language data through its multi-layered, self-attention mechanism."
  ]
}